<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - Mi aplicación ASP.NET</title>
    @Styles.Render("~/Content/css")
    @Scripts.Render("~/bundles/modernizr")
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light">
        <div class="hearder1 col-12 d-flex">
            <div class="col-4">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <div class="form-outline">
                        <input id="search-input" type="search" placeholder="Buscar..." class="inputHeader" />
                    </div>
                    <button id="search-button" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btnHeader">
                        <i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4 logoNav"><img class="logoNavImg" src="~/img/vilvaosBackGroundWhite.png" /></div>
            <div class="col-4 infoRedes d-flex">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/?locale=es_LA"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square redSocial" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/"><i class="fa fa-instagram redSocial" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/?lang=es"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square redSocial" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                <i class="fa fa-user-circle userHeader" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <button class="btnLogin" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Login", "Home")'">Entrar <i class="fa fa-sign-in" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="header2 col-12 d-flex justify-content-around">
            <div class="col-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="linkheader">Inicio</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Cliente", "Home")" class="linkheader">Cliente</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Producto", "Home")" class="linkheader">Producto</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Proveedor", "Home")" class="linkheader">Proveedor</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </nav>

    <div class="body-content">
        @RenderBody()
        <hr />
    </div>

    <footer class="page-footer bg-dark pt-4 footerPage">
        <div class="container-fluid text-center text-md-left contentFooter">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <img class="imgFooter" src="~/img/vilvaosBackGroundBlack.png"/>
            </div>
            <div class=" d-flex justify-content-center redesFooter">
                <div class="redes mt-4">
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/?locale=es_LA"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square redSocialFooter" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/"><i class="fa fa-instagram redSocialFooter" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/?lang=es"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square redSocialFooter" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 d-flex d-flex mt-4 justify-content-around">
                <div class="col-4">
                    <h3 class="text-uppercase">VILVAOS INVENTORIES</h3>
                    <p>En Vilvaos, estamos dedicados a simplificar la gestión de inventarios para tiendas pequeñas. Nuestra pasión es ayudar a las empresas a crecer y prosperar mediante soluciones inteligentes y accesibles.  Nos esforzamos por ser reconocidos por nuestra innovación, facilidad de uso y compromiso con el éxito de nuestros clientes. Únete a nosotros en este viaje hacia la eficiencia y el éxito empresarial.</p>
                </div>
                <hr class="clearfix w-100 d-md-none pb-3">
                <div class="col-4">
                    <h3 class="text-uppercase">CONTACTANOS</h3>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><b>Tel: </b>7777777</li>
                        <li><b>Correo: </b>correoEjemplo@gmail.com</li>
                        <li><b>Direccion: </b>CLL EJM #PLO 10 Bogota Dc</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-copyright text-center py-3">
            <p>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year - Vilvaos Inventories</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    @*@Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jquery")*@
    @*@Scripts.Render("~/bundles/bootstrap")*@
    @*@RenderSection("scripts", required: false)*@
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
